719568f-a.title: Manhattan: East River Drive - 78th Street (East)
719568f-a.text:
Eaat River Drive, north from the foot of East 78th St..
as photographed from the over-pass leading to the Wel-
fare Island Ferry. The structural details appearing are
at 81st Street. Beyond are the apartment buildings that
surround Carl Schurz Park, constituting Gracie Square.
At the left of View 1 is the narrow triangular apartment
house that separates this new thoroughfare from East End
Avenue. For earlier photos of this area, see Marie Curie
Avenue or Exterior Street.
September 29, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
